===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{uncountable}} The feeling of [[happiness]], [[extreme]] [[cheerfulness]].
#: ''They will be a source of strength and joy in your life''.
# {{countable}} An activity etc which causes this feeling.
#: ''The joys and demands of new parents''.

